{"tid":2398620,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺成日話中菜世界第一嘅連登仔係大中華毒上腦","createTime":"2021-02-07T12:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T22:30:22.000Z","uid":39812,"like":29,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4c10fa7421bd3327e2787b3061a250dcbcadcdc7","tid":2398620,"uid":39812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:52:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">屌你老味根本除咗粵菜/潮州菜/淮揚菜/川菜之外其他全部都係垃圾<br />\n嗰啲乜柒湖南山西東北貴州垃圾喺度黐埋嚟認親認戚<br />\n唔係得個辣就得個咸字<br />\n餵狗都唔食<br />\n我食泡菜嘢都唔撚食乜鳩湖南菜啊<br />\n同啲英國嘢德國野黐埋法國菜意大利菜到認親認戚扮西餐有乜嘢分別<br />\n邊個吹奏大中華中餐嘅就係大中華上腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"a8683276ab0728df3947b233903ae8a0ccb8c30d","tid":2398620,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:53:25.000Z","msg":"北方都係面食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d73b9037338c3c64be43568eb9388c4edeb4772","tid":2398620,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:54:16.000Z","msg":"我靜係得上海野覺得OK<br />\n其他野都唔岩食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4c60d13df436e03000faa9ee25ec0a520f7da4","tid":2398620,"uid":39812,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a8683276ab0728df3947b233903ae8a0ccb8c30d","tid":2398620,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:53:25.000Z","msg":"北方都係面食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T12:55:18.000Z","msg":"成班垃圾喺度認親認戚<br />\n細個跟過屋企人去過支那北方旅行餐餐同食屎冇分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi