al/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講歷史有撚用啊<br />\n問題係嗰啲內陸菜日撚日辣油饅頭乜鳩<br />\n垃圾到而家喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f246d1b97248f96ab9fc3367bd77f8b957aab2","tid":2398620,"uid":1230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:08:05.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"351b85a7a60df954de86bf064ea4dd95c73682fd","tid":2398620,"uid":39812,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:08:47.000Z","msg":"大中華上腦嘅連登仔淨係識腐皮<br />\n仲未有人駁倒我<br />\n嗰d乜嘢山西菜湖南菜好食喺邊,憑咩可以同粵菜淮揚菜一齊叫中餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b59ff4a22d7c1fd734fac2f5f128d8b8580bba","tid":2398620,"uid":39812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26f246d1b97248f96ab9fc3367bd77f8b957aab2","tid":2398620,"uid":1230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:08:05.000Z","msg":"係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:09:42.000Z","msg":"太多人大中華上腦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0884df0133eb326f836d3d36bf5d91a058266daf","tid":2398620,"uid":330010,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ee47e1b841fe73e57af9d2ee472f5575fcd43ec","tid":2398620,"uid":283741,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:03:33.000Z","msg":"傳統廣東菜唔係豉油就蠔油，再唔係就南乳，千篇一律，如果唔係靠近年吸收西方食材同煮法，根本不值一提"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:12:12.000Z","msg":"其實廣東菜本身個原意係霖住用少少調味黎引出原材料嗰種鮮味，生抽用黎提鮮，鹽可以突出原材料味道，又唔可以話千篇一律，煮法都有好多種，不過工序太繁複所以太少人用"},{"pid":"3e63c3aac2a6e9a8e9c15e10b8020165c1a23c52","tid":2398620,"uid":39812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:13:55.000Z","msg":"睇嚟好多人鍾意食北方嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5e5